title: Nobody
lyrics:
I'm a preacher
A done decision
Another creature
Has lost its vision
Let it go

Reel it in

For the creature

On television



There's no turning back

To nobody

There's no second chance

No third degree



I'm a fixture

A split decision

A pretty picture

A superstition



Let it go

Cash it in

For the creature

On television



There's no turning back

To nobody

There's no second chance

No third degree

There's no turning back

To nobody

There's no second chance

No third degree
